{"tid":1673724,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中共用淘寶收集香港人數據 唔好再買啦屌！","createTime":"2019-10-24T22:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T23:52:43.000Z","uid":228656,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c2e033bb30f5cab208208015f073146380e7b345","tid":1673724,"uid":228656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T22:56:45.000Z","msg":"小弟試用VPN喺淘寶俾錢<br />\n然後發現一啲啲VPN先比到錢 好明顯取決於中共收唔收到交易數據<br />\n例如：日本，阿爾巴尼亞IP俾唔到錢 但係加拿大 又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">肯定係同收集交易數據有關<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以唔好再喺淘寶買敏感野 瀨！硬！野！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外一用香港IP 就會彈啲嘢引你買<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FsMe805.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFsMe805.jpg&h=fc8ccbb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇咩事都唔好用淘寶啦！</span>"},{"pid":"0c8e839e6e5a08b49f9e4346e3c6ec10f33647d9","tid":1673724,"uid":178440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T22:57:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8037e815c3a8203342f5b8302ac42f2db660ff97","tid":1673724,"uid":252240,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T23:01:37.000Z","msg":"721後，已經刪曬所有大陸app，微信刪埋號，最無代價嘅付出"},{"pid":"07e269cba63ba3ca9fc13ed57e5592bab1becb2c","tid":1673724,"uid":284855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T23:04:40.000Z","msg":"基本上所有大型購物網都會咁做，不過宜家上淘宝真係唔好買敏感嘢"},{"pid":"b87cf1843d48eb9203555cc2d5d68f959ee89e65","tid":1673724,"uid":265739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T23:13:34.000Z","msg":"未del之前<br />\n買日常家用品都自動彈丫叉武器suggestion <br />\n從來無係淘寶search 過<br />\n只有上lighk fb ig有post<br />\n你話幾咁鬼呢"},{"pid":"f128da31586f81992b07bc35ae3f426f103fc732","tid":1673724,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":